  "title": "Registration of ICGV 87157, An Elite Peanut Germplasm with Multiple Resistance to Diseases",
  "abstract": "ICGV 87157, a spanish-type peanut breeding line (Arachis\r\nhypogaea L. subsp. fastigiata var. vulgaris) (Reg. no. GP-\r\n56, PI 556992) that possesses resistance and/or tolerance to\r\nmultiple diseases and insect pests, was released by the\r\nICRISAT Plant Material Identification Committee (PMIC)\r\nin 1990. ICGV 87157 was tested experimentally as\r\nICG(FDRS)4.\r\nICGV 87157",
